<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ</title>
    <link href="/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="container mx-auto p-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-pink-600 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h1><br>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
            <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" />
                <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-semibold">Do you offer custom cakes?</div>
                <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p>Yes! We specialize in custom cakes for all occasions. Contact us for more details.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" />
                <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-semibold">How far in advance should I place an order?</div>
                <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p>We recommend placing your order at least 3 days in advance for standard cakes and 1 week for custom designs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" />
                <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-semibold">Do you have vegan or gluten-free options?</div>
                <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p>Yes, we offer both vegan and gluten-free cakes. Please inform us of any dietary restrictions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" />
                <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-semibold">Do you deliver?</div>
                <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p>Yes, we offer delivery within a 10-mile radius. Additional charges may apply.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
